      "text": "Note: In the PDO example above we have also specified a database (myDB) . PDO require a valid database to connect to. If no database is specified, an exception is thrown.",
      "html": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> In the PDO example above we have also \n<strong>specified a database (myDB)</strong>. PDO require a valid database \nto connect to. If no database is specified, an exception is thrown.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "Tip: A great benefit of PDO is that it has an exception class to handle any problems that may occur in our database queries. If an exception is thrown within the try{ } block, the script stops executing and flows directly to the first catch(){ } block.",
      "html": "<p><strong>Tip:</strong> A great benefit of PDO is that it \nhas an exception class to handle any problems that may \noccur in our database queries. If an exception is thrown within the try{ } block, \nthe script stops executing and flows directly to the first catch(){ } block.</p>"
    },
